  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 1000.0,
      "text": "Hello, this is Crown!"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1000.0,
      "end_time": 3339.0,
      "text": "Today I'm going to talk about \nFaded by Alan Walker!"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8501.0,
      "end_time": 10791.0,
      "text": "Welcome back to Crown's \nEnglish Song Spotlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10791.0,
      "end_time": 14120.0,
      "text": "In the last episode we talked about \nWe Don't Talk Anymore by Charlie Puth"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14120.0,
      "end_time": 18243.0,
      "text": "And today's song is probably the most \nrecommended song ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18243.0,
      "end_time": 19921.0,
      "text": "Faded by Alan Walker!"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31400.0,
      "end_time": 32403.0,
      "text": "Actually, I wanna confess that"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32403.0,
      "end_time": 35641.0,
      "text": "before everyone's recommendation, \nI've never heard of this song"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35642.0,
      "end_time": 38281.0,
      "text": "but seriously, there were way too many people \nrecommending this song"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38281.0,
      "end_time": 40244.0,
      "text": "and after I googled it I realized that...oh god"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40244.0,
      "end_time": 42272.0,
      "text": "This song is hella popular"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42273.0,
      "end_time": 45773.0,
      "text": "This song is about searching for \nsomeone, something, or some place"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45773.0,
      "end_time": 48895.0,
      "text": "Or probably about someone who is lost \nand trying to find himself/herself"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48895.0,
      "end_time": 51723.0,
      "text": "This time I'm also going to explain and \nbreak down the lyrics"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51723.0,
      "end_time": 53881.0,
      "text": "So now let's dive into this top hit song together!"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56974.0,
      "end_time": 59952.0,
      "text": "You were the shadow to my light"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59953.0,
      "end_time": 63485.0,
      "text": "Did you feel us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63485.0,
      "end_time": 67575.0,
      "text": "Another start, you fade away"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67575.0,
      "end_time": 70674.0,
      "text": "Afraid our aim is out of sight"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70674.0,
      "end_time": 76715.0,
      "text": "Wanna see us, alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76715.0,
      "end_time": 78635.0,
      "text": "You were the shadow to my light"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78635.0,
      "end_time": 82840.0,
      "text": "This line could be translate into:\n你伴我如影隨形"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82840.0,
      "end_time": 84243.0,
      "text": "When there is light, there is shadow"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84243.0,
      "end_time": 87556.0,
      "text": "By using \"shadow\" and \"light\" these two words, \nwe can see that"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87556.0,
      "end_time": 89925.0,
      "text": "there is a close relation between them"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89925.0,
      "end_time": 92411.0,
      "text": "Light and shadow exist together and \ncan't be separated"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92412.0,
      "end_time": 94877.0,
      "text": "In fact, there certainly are better words"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94877.0,
      "end_time": 96366.0,
      "text": "to describe two people that can't be parted"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96366.0,
      "end_time": 98588.0,
      "text": "However, he chose the word \"shadow\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98588.0,
      "end_time": 101187.0,
      "text": "giving the feeling of darkness and lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101188.0,
      "end_time": 104117.0,
      "text": "as foretelling that what is going to happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104117.0,
      "end_time": 106497.0,
      "text": "Noted that the past tense \"were\" is used here"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 106497.0,
      "end_time": 110248.0,
      "text": "Which means that how it used to be is \nnot the same right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110248.0,
      "end_time": 113609.0,
      "text": "Afraid our aim is out of sight, wanna see us, alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113609.0,
      "end_time": 115228.0,
      "text": "This line could be translated into:"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115228.0,
      "end_time": 119120.0,
      "text": "害怕我們失去目標，但希望我們不要放棄彼此"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119120.0,
      "end_time": 121957.0,
      "text": "\"Aim\" here is a noun meaning goals and aspirations"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121957.0,
      "end_time": 124208.0,
      "text": "or something to be achieved"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124208.0,
      "end_time": 127478.0,
      "text": "The phrase \"out of sight\" means something is \ntoo far to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 127478.0,
      "end_time": 130776.0,
      "text": "You may often hear the idiom \n\"out of sight, out of mind\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130776.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134757.0,
      "text": "It means something is easy to forget due to \nthe inability to see it"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134758.0,
      "end_time": 136969.0,
      "text": "And the \"alive\" in the line \"wanna see us alive\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136969.0,
      "end_time": 139290.0,
      "text": "Instead of the concept of \"being alive\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139290.0,
      "end_time": 142680.0,
      "text": "it might also implicate the expectation that \ntheir relationship is still \"alive\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142680.0,
      "end_time": 145109.0,
      "text": "which means that they don't give up on each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145109.0,
      "end_time": 148109.0,
      "text": "Where are you now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148109.0,
      "end_time": 150730.0,
      "text": "Was it all in my fantasy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150730.0,
      "end_time": 153331.0,
      "text": "Where are you now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 153331.0,
      "end_time": 156951.0,
      "text": "Were you only imaginary?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156951.0,
      "end_time": 159962.0,
      "text": "Was it all in my fantasy? Were you only imaginary?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159962.0,
      "end_time": 161429.0,
      "text": "This line could be translated into:"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161430.0,
      "end_time": 165680.0,
      "text": "全都只是在我的幻想裡面嗎？難道你只是我的想像嗎？"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 165680.0,
      "end_time": 168641.0,
      "text": "\"Fantasy\" and \"imaginary\" are actually \ntwo very similar words"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168641.0,
      "end_time": 170320.0,
      "text": "They both mean \"not real\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170320.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "What he wanted to express here is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174921.0,
      "text": "Since what he cherished has faded too quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174921.0,
      "end_time": 179382.0,
      "text": "It made him doubt that if all of it is\njust a dream or fantasy"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179382.0,
      "end_time": 181383.0,
      "text": "The repeating \"where are you now\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 181383.0,
      "end_time": 185520.0,
      "text": "resembled the feeling of yelling out loud and \nkeeping on searching"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 185520.0,
      "end_time": 191761.0,
      "text": "These shallow waters never met what I needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 191761.0,
      "end_time": 195692.0,
      "text": "I'm letting go, a deeper dive"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195693.0,
      "end_time": 199153.0,
      "text": "Eternal silence of the sea"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199153.0,
      "end_time": 204864.0,
      "text": "I'm breathing, alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 204864.0,
      "end_time": 207182.0,
      "text": "These shallow waters never met what I needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 207182.0,
      "end_time": 209244.0,
      "text": "I'm letting go, a deeper dive"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209244.0,
      "end_time": 210714.0,
      "text": "This line could be translated into:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210714.0,
      "end_time": 215250.0,
      "text": "這淺水從不是我所求，我要放手去尋找我要的"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 215250.0,
      "end_time": 216424.0,
      "text": "Shallow means \"淺\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216424.0,
      "end_time": 219223.0,
      "text": "And the \"meet\" in \"meet my needs\" means \"符合\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219223.0,
      "end_time": 221544.0,
      "text": "which means \"符合我所要求的\""
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 221544.0,
      "end_time": 223230.0,
      "text": "\"Let go\" is \"放手\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 223230.0,
      "end_time": 225775.0,
      "text": "\"a deeper dive\" is \"往更深的地方潛下去\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 225775.0,
      "end_time": 229405.0,
      "text": "which means to let go and dive into a deeper state"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 229405.0,
      "end_time": 232596.0,
      "text": "Eternal silence of the sea, I'm breathing, alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232596.0,
      "end_time": 237624.0,
      "text": "This line could be translated into:\n在永恆寧靜的海洋中，我活著、呼吸"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237624.0,
      "end_time": 241375.0,
      "text": "\"Eternal\" means \"永遠、永恆\"\n\"silence\" means \"安靜\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 241375.0,
      "end_time": 244397.0,
      "text": "Appreciating the silence under the deep sea"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 244397.0,
      "end_time": 247416.0,
      "text": "and finally feeling able to breath like being alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 247416.0,
      "end_time": 250435.0,
      "text": "Under the bright but faded lights"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250435.0,
      "end_time": 252826.0,
      "text": "You set my heart on fire"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 252826.0,
      "end_time": 255715.0,
      "text": "Where are you now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 255716.0,
      "end_time": 259117.0,
      "text": "Where are you now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 259117.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262123.00000000003,
      "text": "Under the bright but faded lights, you set \nmy heart on fire"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 262123.0,
      "end_time": 263674.0,
      "text": "This line could be translated into:"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263674.0,
      "end_time": 269443.0,
      "text": "在明亮卻開始逐漸消散的燈光下，你曾使我的心熊熊燃燒"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 269443.0,
      "end_time": 272803.0,
      "text": "\"Bright\" is \"亮\", but \"faded\" means \"漸漸消失\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 272803.0,
      "end_time": 277862.0,
      "text": "It used to shine bright like the sunlight, but \nnow it's dull and fading away"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 277862.0,
      "end_time": 282343.0,
      "text": "\"set something on fire\" means \"使某物燃起熊熊烈火\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282343.0,
      "end_time": 285845.0,
      "text": "Where are you now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285845.0,
      "end_time": 287754.0,
      "text": "Atlantis"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287754.0,
      "end_time": 293104.0,
      "text": "Under the sea, under the sea"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 293104.0,
      "end_time": 295813.0,
      "text": "Where are you now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 295814.0,
      "end_time": 299440.0,
      "text": "Another dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 302965.0,
      "text": "The monster's running wild inside of me"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 302965.0,
      "end_time": 308474.0,
      "text": "I'm faded, I'm faded"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308475.0,
      "end_time": 318556.0,
      "text": "So lost, I'm faded"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 318556.0,
      "end_time": 321455.0,
      "text": "Atlantis. Under the sea, under the sea"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 321456.0,
      "end_time": 326516.0,
      "text": "This line could be translated into:\n亞特蘭提斯，在無窮盡的海洋底下"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 326516.0,
      "end_time": 328927.0,
      "text": "\"Atlantis\" is \"亞特蘭提斯\""
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 328927.0,
      "end_time": 332997.0,
      "text": "According to the legend, it's an island with \nhighly developed civilization"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 332997.0,
      "end_time": 336468.0,
      "text": "but eventually sank into the sea and disappeared"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 336468.0,
      "end_time": 339488.0,
      "text": "The use of the story here is because that what he \nhas lost and been looking for"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 339488.0,
      "end_time": 342253.0,
      "text": "is like the lost Atlantis"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 342253.0,
      "end_time": 344878.0,
      "text": "Mysterious and beautiful, but unsearchable"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 344878.0,
      "end_time": 347139.0,
      "text": "The monster's running wild inside of me, I'm faded"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347139.0,
      "end_time": 348436.0,
      "text": "This line could be translated into:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 348436.0,
      "end_time": 352368.0,
      "text": "內心波掏洶湧、情感肆虐，我迷失了自己"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 352368.0,
      "end_time": 355128.0,
      "text": "\"Monster\" here could be implying \nthe demons within his heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 355128.0,
      "end_time": 358647.0,
      "text": "and \"running wild\" means running around crazily"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358648.0,
      "end_time": 361580.0,
      "text": "Maybe it's because he couldn't find what he \nsearched for"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 361580.0,
      "end_time": 364379.0,
      "text": "Therefore it made him go insane and lose himself"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364379.0,
      "end_time": 366290.0,
      "text": "So this is today's English Song Spotlight!"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 366290.0,
      "end_time": 369198.0,
      "text": "If you want to listen to the original song, \nclick the box right here!"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 369198.0,
      "end_time": 371560.0,
      "text": "Alan Walker said that, the best part \nabout this song is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 371560.0,
      "end_time": 374280.0,
      "text": "The meaning and interpretation of the lyrics"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 374280.0,
      "end_time": 376760.0,
      "text": "is not the same for every listeners"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 376760.0,
      "end_time": 379390.0,
      "text": "So welcome everyone to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 379390.0,
      "end_time": 381628.0,
      "text": "what's your interpretation of the song?"
    },
    {
